dct_title_s: Chart of a part of South America surveyed by order of the Rt. Honble. the Lords Commissioners of the Admiralty, under the direction of Capt. P.P. King R.N. during the years 1826-30
dct_description_sm: Relief shown by hachures. Depth shown by soundings. Shows coasts of Patagonia, Tierra del Fuego, and offshore islands. From: Journal of the Royal Geographical Society of London. Vol. 1, (1830-31), pp. 155-75; held in Firestone Library. Call number: G7 .J687 v.1 1830-31 From: Journal of the Royal Geographical Soceity of London.
